# 📊 Evaluation Strategy

## Primary Metrics

```text id="p3m7qx"
1. Recall (extreme class)
2. Balanced Accuracy
3. F1 Score
4. PR AUC
5. ROC AUC
```

Accuracy is NOT primary due to imbalance.

---

# 🧠 DESIGN PRINCIPLES

## DO

* keep steps atomic
* ensure artifact consistency
* rerun only affected steps
* validate outputs per step

## DON'T

* rename artifacts arbitrarily
* mix feature engineering & modeling
* introduce hidden transformations
* skip schema validation stage

---

# ⚠️ IMPORTANT MODEL NOTES

* dataset is highly imbalanced
* leakage control is critical
* target definition is rule-based (not ground truth survey label)
* evaluation must prioritize recall

